title: Patriots-Ravens, Browns, Packers, and where Colin was right & wrong
itunes:title: Patriots-Ravens, Browns, Packers, and where Colin was right & wrong
description:
Colin explains why the Patriots will be fine when it matters, what he likes about the Ravens, his huge mistake about the Browns, why the Packers are in trouble, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Eric Mangini, Trent Dilfer, Michael Vick, and Tony Gonzalez.
